A good way yo find child nodes

how we find it?
- Child Node= Is a node under another node
- Nth-child= multiple nodes under the same level


Find By Child=

    <div id="parent">
<a id="child" href="/child">Child</a></div>

driver.findElement(By.cssSelector("div#parent a"));


Find By Nth-child=

<ul id="list">
<li>One</li>
<li>Two</li>
<li>Three</li>
</ul>

driver.findElement(By.cssSelector("list li:nth-child(n)"));

"n" son los elementos dentro de la lista. Si quiero encontrar el elemento 2, puedo
especificar que n = 2